<br>
If you remember Verant said that POP would not be dedicated only to high end guilds.  So that is where the flaw is.  They stated something that is not true.<br>
<br>
For some reason we have those that got that &quot;Well im better then you complex&quot;.  The feel that no one else should be able to do anything in the game just because they dont belong to a high end guild.  <br>
<br>
It is also flawed because a 65 Mage with no Spectrals or Runes is the same as a lower level Mage in power output.  There should be some way besides waiting until the &quot;Snobs&quot; feel like selling there spells for others to get them.<br>
<br>
I am in a Medium sized guild.  Roughly 45-50 people with average level of 62.  I have majority of my spectrals, but mine came from being invited to hunt with family in high level guilds.  To me, thats bull...everyone regardless of who you a affiliated with should have a way to get Runes and Spectrals.<br>
<br>
Broken words again by Verant<br>
<br>
